<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="73" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,290,352]" pageId="12" pageNumber="73">
Six species of this genus occur in the Palaearctic Region. The females are known only for the 
<typeStatus box="[1219,1267,290,316]" pageId="12" pageNumber="73">type</typeStatus>
species. Three species of this genus are distributed in 
<collectingCountry box="[584,711,326,352]" name="Azerbaijan" pageId="12" pageNumber="73">Azerbaijan</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
